Unit Name: Dry Aromatherapy Diffuser - Nebulizer - USB-C - No Water Required
Webpage description (html):
A Dry Aromatherapy Diffuser is a device that uses no water or heat to disperse essential oils into the air. Instead, it uses nebulization to break down the oils into tiny molecules which can be easily inhaled. It is a popular choice for people who want to experience the benefits of essential oils without the use of heat or humidity.

These diffusers are generally considered to be more convenient and safer than those that use heat or water, as they do not pose a risk of burns or spills. They also tend to preserve the therapeutic properties of the essential oils better than other methods.

10 ml bottle included.

Unit Name: Large Volcano Effect Aroma Diffuser (plug) Two Colours
Webpage description (html):
Large Volcano Effect Aroma Diffuser with a capacity of 560 ml.

Add certain amount of water and few drops of your favourite essential oil to elevate your aromatherapy experience. The light mist this humidifier produces creates an amazing 3D flame or volcanic effect, allowing you to adjust between warm yellow flames and cool blue flames.

Powered by an ultrasonic motor, this diffuser operates quietly. It can be operated effortlessly with a single button or conveniently switched between various modes and effects using the included remote control.

Safety and convenience are assured with the timer function and built-in protection chip. You can set the humidifier to turn off automatically every 3 or 6 hours, ensuring peace of mind during your restful sleep. The built-in protective chip ensures the unit switches off when the water level is low, preventing any potential risks. 

Its versatility makes it perfect for use at home, hotels, schools, bedrooms, baby rooms, yoga studios, air-conditioned spaces, and dry areas. Enhance your space with the soothing fragrance of your favourite essential oils and create a delightful relaxing atmosphere. 

NB: To ensure the longevity of your product, avoid cleaning it directly with tap water or wetting the power input, as this may lead to a short circuit. We recommend using a cotton cloth for cleaning purposes.

Unit Name: Single Waterless Oil Nebulizer - USB to C Yellow
Webpage description (html):
Rechargable Waterless Oil Nebulizer - easy to operate, sutaible for 10ml or 20ml bottles. 

How to charge:

Use output voltage DC5V, computer USB interface, USB interface adapter or car charger with USB interface. The red light flashes when charging; when fully charged, the indicator is always green.

In the power-on state, if the remaining batttery power is lower than 20% the light will flash quickly in any mode, prompting need to charge. 

It takes 2 - 3 hours to fully charge the diffuser.  

How to use:

Push the nozzle out from the bottom of the diffuser gently.

Insert any essential oil to the bottle, and then install the bottle back to the nozzle. Attention to the mark of the position direction on diffuser. 

Smart mode: Short press the top button to turn on, the left light is on white which means that the machine enters the smart mode and starts/stops. 

Manual mode: Short press to turn on, the middle light is on white which means that is in light aroma mode, press again, the right light is on changing to strong aroma mode.

Recommended to use only with essential oils.

Dimensions: 105mmx 65mm

Unit Name: Mini Single Waterless Oil Nebulizer - USB to C - movement dectector
Webpage description (html):
This product is suitable for 10ml bottled essential oils.

For the first use, remove the 'dust cover' and turn the diffuser over and insert the essential oil bottle

How to use: 

Turn the diffuser over and insert the essential oil bottle, turn clockwise to tightem, and counterclockwise to loosen the bottle. (Note: When installing essential oil, please do not remove the throttle valve.)

Rotate the diffuser vertically, long press the switch button for 2 seconds to start/stop the diffuser, short press to switch gears. 

The first long press (yellow light): the diffuser works for 2 seconds and then works for 2seconds each time it sense motion. 

Press the second time (green light) light fragrance mode: work for 2 seconds, with an interval of 10 minutes.

Press the third time (blue light) fragrance mode: work for 2 seconds with and internal of 5 minutes. 

Press the fourth time (white light) for a strong fragrance: work for 2 seconds with an interval of 1 minute. 

The indicator light is on during charging (red light) and turns off when fully charged. 

Long press for 2s to power off. 

Sensing range: 3 meters / 120degrees

Applicable area: 50-80m2

Dimensions: 84,6mm x 74,2mm

Unit Name: Double (switchable) Essential Oil Waterless Nebulizer- USB to C
Webpage description (html):
Double Essential Oil Waterless Nebulizer doesn't need water or heat. It directly atomizes the essential oil into particles of 1-3 nanometers, which does not harm the oil's molecular structure and enhances its fragrance. 

For the first use, gently push the button at the bottom with your fingers. Remove the empty bottle and replace it with new bottle of essential oil, then put the nozzle. Install back to the original product. The triangle symbols on the nozzle need to match each other.

Note: When replacing the essential oil bottle, refer to the following figure: If the essential oil is not used up during the replacement, please erect the machine. Tighten the nozzle assembly and install it in case it cannot be removed.

The product is charged with 5V DC voltage, which can be charged with a USB port adapter or a car charger with a USB port. When the product is charging, thy Type-C charging light is on, when battery is fully charged, the charging light is always red.

In the power-on state, when the remaining battery capacity is less than 15%, the charging light above the Type-C will light up in red and flash 3 times in 1s (quick flashing) indicating that it needs to be charged.

Suitable for 10 ml bottled essential oils.

Unit Name: Urban Aroma Diffuser White & Bronze- USB - Colour Change
Webpage description (html):
Night Light Aromatherapy Humifidier with night light function.

Use a type C connector to a power supply.

Dimensions: 12x8,8x8,8cm

Water tank capacity: 120ml

How to use:

Add water before using this product, it's forbidden to use the humidification function in the case of water shortage. 

When claning the product, please do not wash directly with a tap to avoid the possibility of product short curcuit. 

Power on, RGB lights flash once each (0.5 seconds each)

Short press once to start spraying, the fan will rotate, and the RGB lights will turn on colourful cycles, and then short press again to shut down.

Unit Name: Clear Humidifer Mondo Planet - USB - Colour Change (down light)
Webpage description (html):
The Clear Humidifier Mondo Planet has a modern, transparent design that appeals to contemporary aesthetics and is designed to maintain optimal humidity levels, facilitating better breathing and healthier skin.

How to use:

Light Button: The first click is warm white light, the second click is all lights on, the third click is running lamp mode, and the fourth clock is off light mode.

Spray Button: Press and hold the first time to turn on the spray, and press and hold again to turn off the spray.

Water adding method: Grasp the bottom of water tank with your hand, open the water tank in the direction indicated by label and add water. After adding water, lock the inside of the water tank. Align the identification with the main body, rotate clockwise to lock the water tank and counter clockwise to open the water tank.

Note: This machine is equipped with two cotton swabs (one for backup). For first use, please remove the sleeve and cotton swab from the accessory bag. After fully soaking the cotton swab in the water, install it into the sleeve and fix the sleeve containing cotton swab on the inner bracket of the water tank above the maximum water level. Tighten the water tank and follow the instructions to start working.

White Nano Mist Face Fan & Spray is designed to offer on-the-go hydration and refreshing mist, making it a must-have addition to your inventory.
